import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';

class BasementRenovationsInMississauga extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovations in Mississauga</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovations in Mississauga" />
        <div className="container">
          <p>At AGM Basements, we understand the importance of finding a company who is going to turn your basement remodelling and basement finishing dream into a stress-free process. In Mississauga alone, we have already completed over 250 basement renovations in homes that vary in size, age, and needs. When you choose AGM, you become part of a team that goes above and beyond to make your vision a reality.</p>

          <h3>One Stop Shop</h3>

          <p>AGM Basements is essentially your one stop shop for all basement remodelling needs. We offer a wide range of services, meaning that you won't have to hire multiple basement contractors.</p>

          <p>We understand that every project we take on is unique. We pride ourselves on our versatility, meaning that we really do work with you from day one to make your vision come true.</p>

          <p>Once we take on a project, we have a large team of people who will dedicate their time to it. This team includes a dedicated project manager, a professional team of interior designers, experienced basement builders, master electricians, and finally a professional cleaning team who will finish up and leave your new space looking like a model home.</p>

          <h3>Health and Safety</h3>

          <p>As well as undergoing regular health and safety checks, our basement builders and technicians offer a professional radon detection service. Radon gas is radioactive and one of the leading causes of lung cancer. If pockets of radon gas are present on your property, they are most likely to be disturbed during renovations. This is why we are proud to offer a service that is so vital to protecting the health of both yourself and your family.</p>

          <h3>Mississauga Services</h3>

          <p>When looking at basement renovation companies, it is important to find one that works perfectly for you. We are proud to have a wide range of versatile services that can be tailor made just for you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Bathrooms</li>
            <li>Kitchens</li>
            <li>Saunas</li>
            <li>Theatres</li>
            <li>Offices</li>
            <li>Play Rooms</li>
            <li>Gyms</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Why AGM Basements?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Experienced and master tradesmen</li>
            <li>Professional design consultations and drawings at no additional cost</li>
            <li>We guarantee your satisfaction – we don't get paid until you are completely satisfied</li>
            <li>We will pay you if the project isn't finished on time.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We pride ourselves in going above and beyond for our clients, and our reputation reflects just that. We welcome you to attend one of our many open houses and finishing showcases, and are able to provide you with a long list of referrals.</p>

          <h3>Free Estimate</h3>

          <p>Do you have something specific in mind? Perhaps you have a space with a lot of potential but can't think what to do with it? Just give us a call! We can talk you through the whole process and give you a free estimate.         </p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationsInMississauga;
